      "title": "Freedom Party support for Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided to vote in favor of Member of Parliament Dallas Alahapperuma who has joined as a candidate for the election of a new President through the Parliament in the election to be held tomorrow (20th). The party had earlier decided not to support any candidate."
      ],
